Buster Merryfield https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buster_Merryfield 0 Harry "Buster" Merryfield (27 November 1920 – 23 June 1999) was an English actor best known for starring as Uncle Albert in the BBC comedy Only Fools and Horses.
